'''Jonathan Abbatt''' is a Canadian chemist currently at the [[University of Toronto]] and an Elected Fellow of the [[American Geophysical Union]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.chem.utoronto.ca/ppl/faculty_profile.php?id=1 |title=Jonathan Abbatt |publisher=utoronto.ca |accessdate=April 25, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://honors.agu.org/honorsfellow/1271-abbatt/ |title=Jonathan Abbatt |publisher=agu.org |accessdate=April 25, 2017}}</ref> His work mainly focuses on chemical processes in the atmosphere.<ref>{{cite web|title=Home|url=https://www.abbattgroup.ca/|website=Abbatt Group UofT|accessdate=24 November 2017}}</ref>

