'''Tor Ørvig''' (1916 &ndash; 1994)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://libris.kb.se/hitlist?q=WFRF:(%C3%98rvig+Tor+1916+1994)&d=libris&m=10&p=1&hist=true&noredirect=true|title=LIBRIS - sökning: WFRF:(Ørvig Tor 1916 1994)|website=libris.kb.se}}</ref> was a Norwegian-born [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[paleontologist]] who explored the [[histology]] of early [[vertebrates]]. He was professor at the [[Swedish Museum of Natural History]] in [[Stockholm]] and member of the [[Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences]].

